has sanctioned Rs. 49.87 crore to be paid to farmers in district Hisar as compensation for damage to crops due to hailstorm and heavy rains during Kharif 2019, Rabi 2019-20 and Rabi 2020.
  @cmohry
(Posted on Twitter by @DiprHaryana)
title_post_text: Haryana Government @mlkhattar has sanctioned Rs. 49.87 crore to be paid to farmers in district Hisar as compensation for damage to crops due to hailstorm and heavy rains during Kharif 2019, Rabi 2019-20 and Rabi 2020.   @cmohry ()
translation: Haryana Government @mlkhattar has sanctioned Rs. 49.87 crore to be paid to farmers in district Hisar as compensation for damage to crops due to hailstorm and heavy rains during Kharif 2019, Rabi 2019-20 and Rabi 2020.   @cmohry ()
